{"tid":492962,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"網台MyRadio控熱血時報網台主持誹謗","createTime":"2017-12-08T05:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T16:38:10.000Z","uid":114010,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d63c734b0d1e749289bd0f1e24307df577e79574","tid":492962,"uid":114010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:07:14.000Z","msg":"由前立法會議員黃毓民任董事兼股東的網台「MyRadio」，昨入稟高院控告熱血時報網台主持伍淑儒誹謗，指伍在其個人facebook專頁上寫有「My Radio繼續搞你地D黃賭毒啦！報返落後代的！」。「My radio」指相關言論誹謗，嚴重損害其聲譽和生意，要求法庭頒令對方禁止發布相關言論、道歉和賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://原告Myradio.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%8E%9F%E5%91%8AMyradio.HK&d=jDd7n1Vz9sOp%2FOQjG5TxkTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=fbe2e603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">原告Myradio.HK</a> Limited指被告於本年9月27日發布該言論，最少有2人轉載、95人作出回應，言論令人覺得原告經營色情、賭博和毒品生意，影響原告聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n原告指其網台節目「毓民踩場」、「贏爆洲際杯」、「贏爆全世界」廣受好評，是主要收入來源，但因被告的言論而收入下跌，認為作為競爭者的被告是故意發佈言論打擊原告。原告在10月透過律師去信被告要求對方道歉，但沒任何回覆，遂入稟興訟。"},{"pid":"eff885d39488c47036f607c2fda81c9860cb0218","tid":492962,"uid":8129,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:19:10.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗"},{"pid":"35571294ac070035ff445bcf237b11486d9cc46d","tid":492962,"uid":29862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"唔告黃洋達？"},{"pid":"8be2b52193abd5ebb077cef026cd4114daa14d42","tid":492962,"uid":156659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60ca7dd6d987bee8f110020838cc356fdda9eb9","tid":492962,"uid":50984,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:56:27.000Z","msg":"告誹謗呢d咁燒錢既官司汪洋一定會割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08625cb551d4493445ce60facf577836e4fd3b20","tid":492962,"uid":50984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:57:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗咬狗</blockquote><br />\n話知佢啦總之有人收拾熱狗班垃圾何樂而不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030da24f1a3e17a38f7fe39c73c85a953b07db13","tid":492962,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>告誹謗呢d咁燒錢既官司汪洋一定會割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條傻婆喺佢自己fb寫，熱狗唔駛上身，光頭達應該開多條課金link仲有水抽下"},{"pid":"86573107edc4171b45ed52bb2ae328bfa21d7931","tid":492962,"uid":96894,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>告誹謗呢d咁燒錢既官司汪洋一定會割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未必會割蓆, 鳩達最少應該會開多條課金 link 幫下伍淑儒 ( 記住俾 $100 有 $ 30 俾鳩達作為行政費用 ) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187b6ded2be6468345e55c7e0c3ac446332ecc68","tid":492962,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9c1d3e2cf4ddf2e12e490dcafaa33cfcc52f3b","tid":492962,"uid":1984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"抵喇"},{"pid":"aa0a1d9beac05d13a6aae8b5aba875d1858f39c5","tid":492962,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:46:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e8cee7d9614e2ce0e3a5927f971b25b180516ab","tid":492962,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60d28812aa99ecbcd497bbb741fb758cff5a74db","tid":492962,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵喇